    <div class="campus">
        <h2>Campus Life</h2>
        <p>Karunya is a residential University. Students are housed in thirteen different, well-furnished hostels with all the necessary facilities provided within the campus. Students need not look far for any amenity that they may require during their stay on campus. From a hospital to a bank, from dine-outs to utility stores, from Xerox shops to photo studios, you name it we have it on campus!</p>
    </div> 
